- Megan?
- Oh, my god.

01:04:30.333 --> 01:04:31.583
Megan.

01:04:31.667 --> 01:04:32.750
She's awake.

01:04:32.833 --> 01:04:33.833
Megan.

01:04:36.167 --> 01:04:37.667
