01:06:33.667 --> 01:06:35.958
Tracy.

01:06:36.042 --> 01:06:40.458
Dad, why did she
say she's my stepmom?

01:06:43.792 --> 01:06:45.625
Baby, I need you to
stay with your grandma.

01:06:45.708 --> 01:06:46.708
Okay.

01:06:55.833 --> 01:06:56.833
Sorry.

01:07:12.833 --> 01:07:15.333
Just the man
