What?

01:07:43.625 --> 01:07:45.542
You're coming with us.

01:07:45.625 --> 01:07:46.917
Tracy Jacobs, all right?

01:07:47.042 --> 01:07:48.500
I keep saying-- Tracy Jacobs.

01:07:48.583 --> 01:07:50.250
