Brittany!

01:13:10.542 --> 01:13:11.958
Brittany.

01:13:12.042 --> 01:13:14.958
Brittany, where are you?

01:13:15.042 --> 01:13:16.042
Brittany.

01:13:17.000 --> 01:13:18.000
Brittany.

