All right, come here.
Come here.

01:13:33.000 --> 01:13:33.875
Come on, come on.

01:13:33.958 --> 01:13:35.042
I got you.

01:13:35.125 --> 01:13:36.417
I got you.

01:13:36.500 --> 01:13:37.750
All right, all right.

