Again?

01:16:15.667 --> 01:16:17.250
Do you?

01:16:17.333 --> 01:16:18.333
Answer me!

01:16:38.000 --> 01:16:38.917
How's it going?

01:16:40.875 --> 01:16:43.333
Brittany.

01:16:43.417 --> 01:16:45.542
Brittany, wait, wait.

01:16:45.625 --> 01:16:46.583
Don't go in there.
Don't go in there.

